Author: HTDpetrichor
Text: My BMI is the same as yours and I can't tell if in fat or skinny.  Same with my height, I'm 5 ft 4 and because it's average height I get confused if I'm tall or short.

Author: grossenten98
Text: There’s no in between because no one knows how to be satisfied in this world. And life is a game of “I’m better/worse than the next” -  My BMI is 17.8 and I’m still feeling crappie about my body. Idek wtf to say about it really. It’s madness, pure madness.
